			<h2>Who We Are</h2>
			<div class="team-member team-member-head">
				<div class="team-member-image">
					<img src="/wp-content/themes/hca/img/image.jpg"/>
				</div>
				<div class="team-member-text">
					<h3>Doctor Virginie Green</h3>
					<p>Quid faciat laetas segetes quo sidere terram vertere, Mycenas, ulmisque adiungere vites conveniat quae curum boum qui cultus habendo sit pecori apibus quanta experientia parcis, hinc canere incipiam; vos, o clarissima mundi, lumina, labentes</p>
